Description: Demonstrates the use of multiple R packages for reproducible project management environment for psychological research. This includes using xprmntr and jsPsych (a JavaScript library) for designing web and lab-based experiments. papaja for writing APA papers. The tidyverse for and R Markdown for general data-wrangling, analysis, and notetaking. And, pkgdown and R package templates for file management, function and data sharing, and general dissemination via webpages using GitHub.
